86inline void GetSwizzleIndex(TVector<int> *indexOut) {}
87
88template <typename T, typename... ArgsT>
89void GetSwizzleIndex(TVector<int> *indexOut, T arg, ArgsT... args)
90{
91 indexOut->push_back(arg);
92 GetSwizzleIndex(indexOut, args...);
93}
94
95template <typename... ArgsT>
96TIntermSwizzle *CreateSwizzle(TIntermTyped *reference, ArgsT... args)
97{
98 TVector<int> swizzleIndex;
99 GetSwizzleIndex(&swizzleIndex, args...);
100 return new TIntermSwizzle(reference, swizzleIndex);
101}
